<p><strong>What is expected</strong>: tool to do task on each item, one by one in the listbox.</p>  <p><strong>What is happening:</strong> tool does the task only on the user selected item in the listbox. And nothing else.</p>  <p>Code:</p>  <pre><code> int index;         string item;         foreach (int i in listBox1.SelectedIndices)         {             index = listBox1.SelectedIndex;             item = listBox1.Items[index].ToString();             texteditor.Documents.Open(@item);         } </code></pre>